Jon B. RIVERA and United Services Automobile Association, a foreign corporation, Petitioners, v. Richard WEINFELD, Respondent. No. 44060. Supreme Court of Florida. Dec. 20, 1973. CARLTON, C. J., and ADKINS, BOYD and DEKLE, JJ., concur. McCAIN, J., dissents.

Rehearing Denied March 18, 1974.
